Jiangxi Province; Nanping City to Hengfeng City in Jiangxi; Kanshi
Town to Meizhou City in Guangdong Province; from Longyan City to
Jiangxi's Ganzhou City; from Fuzhou, its provincial capital, to
Wenzhou City in Zhejiang Province; and from Xiamen to Guangdong's
Chaozhou. 
