<HEADLINE> Syrian President Calls for Arab-Muslim Solidarity </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, August 1 (Xinhua) -- The visiting Syrian President
Hafiz al-Assad today called for solidarity between Arab and
