in 22.45 seconds.
</P>
<P>
Double Olympic silver medalist Gary Hall finished a
disappointing fifth in 22.91.
</P>
<P>
Amanda Adkins won the women's 200-meter backstroke in 2:12.62.
</P>
<P>
The seven-day national championships are also the U.S. team
trials for the FINA world championships in Perth, Australia, the
Pan Pacific Championships in Fukuoka, Japan, and the World
University Games in Sicily, Italy. 
