international oil majors on a 50:50 equity basis and the idea is
to acquire technology and then get into deep sea exploration in a
big way, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
ONGC has been allocated three deep sea blocks on a nomination
basis and it will explore these blocks on its own. The tie-up with
foreign companies will be for all other deep sea blocks that ONGC
might be awarded through international competitive bidding, the
sources added.  
