<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 31 (Xinhua) -- Peter Fleming and Gene Mayer
survived stiff battle from Roscoe Tanner and John Fitzgerald 7-6
(8-6), 7-6 (7-4) and advanced to the doubles championship match at
the Challenge over-35 tournament in Colorado Springs, Colorado
Thursday.
</P>
